# Allowlisting gitignore template for GO projects prevents us
# from adding various unwanted local files, such as generated
# files, developer configurations or IDE-specific files etc.
#
# Recommended: Go.AllowList.gitignore

# Ignore everything
*

# But not these files...
!/.gitignore
!/.gitattributes
!/.dockerignore

!*.go
!go.sum
!go.mod
!handlers/scraper/dictionary.bin

!README.md
!TESTING.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!SECURITY.md
!AGENTS.md
!.env.example
!LICENSE
!Dockerfile
!auth-helper/*.py
!auth-helper/Dockerfile
!auth-helper/requirements.txt
!Caddyfile
!docker-compose.example.yml
!scripts/*.yml
!scripts/*.yaml
!scripts/*.sh

# Never track local/session secrets.
secrets/
**/secrets/
*cookie*
!scripts/update-instagram-cookie.sh
*.env
!.env.example

# !Makefile

# ...even if they are in subdirectories
!*/

# Local agent/plugin installations.
.agents/
